<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.3">
<l>cempoṉ matiḷcūḻ teṉṉilaṅkaik kiṟaivaṉ ciraṅka ḷaiyiraṇṭum</l>
<l>umpar vāḷik kilakkāka vutirtta vuravō ṉūrpōlum</l>
<l>kompi lārnta mātavimēl kōti mēynta vaṇṭiṉaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>ampa rāvuṅ kaṇmaṭavā raimpā laṇaiyu maḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the stalwart [lord] who fell the ten heads,</l>
<l rend="indent">the targets for his lofty arrows,</l>
<l>Of the ruler of Lankā to the south, surrounded by rose-gold walls,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr where swarms of bees, which browse,</l>
<l rend="indent">scratching on mādhavi [creepers] which spread on the branches,</l>
<l>Gather on the hair  of simple [girls] with eyes that pierce [like] arrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
